    publishDate: 'July 21, 2026',
    excerpt: 'When your solar company goes out of business, the consequences can be severe: voided warranties, no maintenance, and continuing payment obligations. This comprehensive guide covers everything homeowners need to know when their solar installer or lender goes bankrupt — including Freedom Forever, SunPower, Sunnova, and other recent bankruptcies.',
